creator: Kakao Corporation
descriptionHtml:
Kakaobus provides you with real-time bus and bus stop information of 57 Korean cities.

* Real-time bus arrival information
* Bus route information with real-time bus location
* Departure Alarm
Set up the departure alarm to receive notifications five minutes, three minutes or one minute before the bus arrives at your stop.
* Arrival Alarm
Set an alarm to make sure you get off at the right stop.
* Bus Arrival Notification
You can get notifications for buses at a certain day and time without having to set them manually every time.
* Suggestions based on your current location : Nearby Stops, Night Buses Nearby, Direct Bus to Home, Kakao Taxi

Continued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.

* Customer Service Center
- Mail : bus@kakaocorp.com
- TEL : 1577-3321
descriptionShort: Kakaobus provides you with real-time information of 57 Korean cities

creator: Kakao Mobility Corp.
descriptionHtml:
Check real-time arrival times and schedules for buses and subways quickly.
Get useful information to make your daily commute more convenient.

◈ Nationwide bus arrival information
Find bus information for major cities, such as Seoul, Gyeonggi, and Incheon.
◈ Nationwide subway arrival and route information
Check subway arrival times and find routes for Seoul, Gwangju, Daegu, Daejeon, and Busan.
◈ Quickly access your saved bus and subway arrival times from the home screen
Bookmark your frequently used bus stops and subway stations for quick access from the home screen.
◈ Bus and subway ride notifications
Stay informed with ride notifications that alert you when to get on and off, so you never miss your stop.

[Note]
- Using ride notifications may increase battery consumption due to background location usage.
descriptionShort: Kakaobus provides you with real-time information of 57 Korean cities
